data.description: Ready....set....sold!  Don't let that four letter word cause you blurt out other four letter words by missing out on this one.  Located in Lakeside School District this property has everything you need and more.  3 nice sized bedrooms with 2 full baths on the main level, then downstairs has space to host another bedroom, playroom, or media room with a half bath and access to the backyard.  Mature landscaping creating a backyard oasis for those cookouts while hanging with family and friends.  Come take a look and claim this one as "home".  See agent remarks regarding possession.
